<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَاذْكُرْنَ مَا يُتْلَى فِي بُيُوتِكُنَّ مِنْ آيَاتِ اللهِ وَالْحِكْمَةِ , إِنَّ اللهَ كَانَ لَطِيفًا خَبِيرًا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١١٧:</span> قَالَ قَتَادَةُ: <span class="c3">{آيَاتِ اللهِ}</span>: القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَالحِكْمَةُ}</span>: السُّنَّةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
